# Nigeria Legal Marketplace - Environment Variables Template

# 1. Supabase Storage Configuration
# Find these in Supabase Settings > API
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-id.supabase.co
SUPABASE_KEY=your-service-role-key-here

# 2. Mock Test Data (For Verification Flow)
# The system uses these mocked records to simulate official identity lookup:
# NIN: 12345670027 -> Name: Adamu Musa
# NIN: 12345671234 -> Name: Chinelu Okafor
# Any other 11-digit numeric NIN -> Name: Verified Citizen

# 3. Local Development
# If SUPABASE_URL/KEY are missing, the system falls back to local storage:
# storage/uploads/
